## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="2fde8-102">XML 架构元素定义名为`xsi:choice`用于定义可以包含实例中的只有一个子级的复杂元素 (maxoccurs = 1)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2fde8-102">The XML schema element definition named `xsi:choice` is used to define a complex element that can contain only one child in an instance (maxoccurs = 1).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2fde8-103">该子级可以是多个类型之一，并可具有多个名称之一。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2fde8-103">That child can be one of several types, and it can have one of several names.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2fde8-104">每个名称都与特定的类型; 相关联但是，多个名称可以使用相同的类型相关联。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2fde8-104">Each name is associated with a specific type; however, several names can be associated with the same type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2fde8-105">因此，此类元素的实例是不明确的。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2fde8-105">Because of this, an instance of such an element is indistinct.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2fde8-106">例如，考虑以下架构片断，用于定义此类不明确的元素，名为`MyChoice`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2fde8-106">For example, consider the following schema fragment that defines such an indistinct element named `MyChoice`.</span></span>  
  
```  
<xsd:complexType name="MyChoice">  
 <xsd:sequence>  
 <xsd:choice minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="1">  
 <xsd:element minOccurs="1" maxOccurs="1" name="ChoiceOne" type="xsd:string" />  
 <xsd:element minOccurs="1" maxOccurs="1" name="ChoiceTwo" type="xsd:string" />  
 </xsd:choice>  
 </xsd:sequence>  
</xsd:complexType>  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="2fde8-107"><xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlChoiceIdentifierAttribute>允许您将一个特殊的枚举值分配到每个实例的成员。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2fde8-107">The <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlChoiceIdentifierAttribute> allows you to assign a special enumeration value to each instance of the member.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2fde8-108">您必须创建在枚举自己或者它可以通过生成[XML 架构定义工具 (Xsd.exe)](~/docs/standard/serialization/xml-schema-definition-tool-xsd-exe.md)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2fde8-108">You must either create the enumeration yourself or it can be generated by the [XML Schema Definition Tool (Xsd.exe)](~/docs/standard/serialization/xml-schema-definition-tool-xsd-exe.md).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2fde8-109">下面的 C# 代码演示如何<xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlChoiceIdentifierAttribute>应用于`Item`字段;<xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlChoiceIdentifierAttribute.MemberName%2A>属性标识包含进一步用于检测选择枚举的字段。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2fde8-109">The following C# code shows how the <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlChoiceIdentifierAttribute> is applied to an `Item` field; the <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlChoiceIdentifierAttribute.MemberName%2A> property identifies the field that contains the enumeration that is further used to detect the choice.</span></span>  
  
```  
public class Choices{  
 [XmlChoiceIdentifier("ItemType")]  
 [XmlChoiceIdentifier("ChoiceOne")]  
 [XmlChoiceIdentifier("ChoiceTwo")]  
 public string MyChoice;  
  
 // Do not serialize this next field:  
 [XmlIgnore]  
 public ItemChoiceType ItemType;  
}  
// Do not include this enumeration in the XML schema.  
[XmlType(IncludeInSchema = false)]  
public enum ItemChoiceType{  
 ChoiceOne,  
 ChoiceTwo,  
}  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="2fde8-110">在此代码后，您可以序列化并进行反序列化此类设置`ItemType`字段为合适的枚举。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2fde8-110">When this code is in place, you can serialize and deserialize this class by setting the `ItemType` field to an appropriate enumeration.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2fde8-111">例如，若要序列化`Choice`类，C# 代码如下所示。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2fde8-111">For example, to serialize the `Choice` class, the C# code resembles the following.</span></span>  
  
```  
Choices mc = new Choices();  
mc.MyChoice = "Item Choice One";  
mc.ItemType = ItemChoiceType.ChoiceOne;  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="2fde8-112">当反序列化，则 C# 代码如下所示：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2fde8-112">When deserializing, the C# code resembles the following:</span></span>  
  
```  
MyChoice mc = (MyChoice) myXmlSerializer.Deserialize(myReader);  
if(mc.ItemType == ItemChoiceType.ChoiceOne)  
 {  
     // Handle choice one.  
 }  
if(mc.ItemType == ItemChoiceType.ChoiceTwo)  
 {  
     // Handle choice two.  
 }  
if(mc.ItemType != null)  
 {  
     throw CreateUnknownTypeException(mc.Item);  
 }  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="2fde8-113">没有第二个方案时<xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlChoiceIdentifierAttribute>使用。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2fde8-113">There is a second scenario when the <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlChoiceIdentifierAttribute> is used.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2fde8-114">在以下架构中，成员是返回项的数组的字段 (maxOccurs ="unbounded")。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2fde8-114">In the following schema, the member is a field that returns an array of items (maxOccurs="unbounded").</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2fde8-115">数组可以包含对象的第一个选项 ("D-a-t-a")，和的第二个选项 ("MoreData")。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2fde8-115">The array can contain objects of the first choice ("D-a-t-a"), and of the second choice ("MoreData").</span></span>  
  
```  
<xsd:complexType name="MyChoice">  
 <xsd:sequence>  
 <xsd:choice minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="unbounded">  
 <xsd:element minOccurs="1" maxOccurs="1" name="D-a-t-a" type="xsd:string" />  
 <xsd:element minOccurs="1" maxOccurs="1" name="MoreData" type="xsd:string" />  
 </xsd:choice>  
 </xsd:sequence>  
</xsd:complexType>  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="2fde8-116">生成的类然后使用字段返回项的数组。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2fde8-116">The resulting class then uses a field to return an array of items.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2fde8-117">相应的数组中每个项`ItemChoiceType`还必须找到枚举。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2fde8-117">For each item in the array, a corresponding `ItemChoiceType` enumeration must also be found.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2fde8-118">返回的数组中包含的匹配枚举`ItemsElementName`字段。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2fde8-118">The matching enumerations are contained in the array returned by the `ItemsElementName` field.</span></span>  
  
```  
public class MyChoice {  
 [System.Xml.Serialization.XmlElementAttribute("D-a-t-a", typeof(string), IsNullable=false)]  
 [System.Xml.Serialization.XmlElementAttribute("MoreData", typeof(string), IsNullable=false)]  
 [System.Xml.Serialization.XmlChoiceIdentifierAttribute("ItemsElementName")]  
 public string[] Items;  
 [System.Xml.Serialization.XmlElementAttribute(IsNullable=false)]  
 [System.Xml.Serialization.XmlIgnoreAttribute()]  
 public ItemsChoiceType[] ItemsElementName;  
}  
[System.Xml.Serialization.XmlTypeAttribute(IncludeInSchema=false)]  
public enum ItemsChoiceType {  
 [System.Xml.Serialization.XmlEnumAttribute("D-a-t-a")]  
 Data,  
 MoreData,  
}  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="2fde8-119">当反序列化包括一系列选择的对象，使用的控件结构 (如 if......其他结构) 来确定如何反序列化特定值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2fde8-119">When deserializing an object that includes a range of choices, use a control structure (such as an if...then...else structure) to determine how to deserialize a particular value.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2fde8-120">在控件结构中，检查枚举值和反序列化的值将相应地。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2fde8-120">In the control structure, check the enumeration value and deserialize the value accordingly.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="2fde8-121">下面的示例序列化类名为`Choices`包括两个字段，`MyChoice`和`ManyChoices`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2fde8-121">The following example serializes a class named `Choices` that includes two fields, `MyChoice` and `ManyChoices`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2fde8-122"><xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlChoiceIdentifierAttribute>应用于指定每个字段 (通过<xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlChoiceIdentifierAttribute.MemberName%2A>属性)，可获取或设置一个枚举，检测到的成员值的另一个类成员。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2fde8-122">The <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlChoiceIdentifierAttribute> is applied to each field that specifies (through the <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlChoiceIdentifierAttribute.MemberName%2A> property) another class member that gets or sets an enumeration that detects the member value.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2fde8-123">`MyChoice`字段可以与在中找到相应的枚举成员设置为单个值，`EnumType`字段。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2fde8-123">The `MyChoice` field can be set to a single value, with a corresponding enumeration member found in the `EnumType` field.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2fde8-124">`ManyChoices`字段会返回对象的数组。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2fde8-124">The `ManyChoices` field returns an array of objects.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2fde8-125">`ChoiceArray`字段返回一个枚举值的数组。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2fde8-125">The `ChoiceArray` field returns an array of enumeration values.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2fde8-126">每个数组成员`ManyChoices`字段中，通过返回的数组中找到相应成员`ChoiceArray`字段。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2fde8-126">For each array member in the `ManyChoices` field, a corresponding member is found in the array returned by the `ChoiceArray` field.</span></span>  
  
